T|Novi|0|ROAS: No signal — Day 4 of confirmed pipeline stall. ka's June 11 diagnosis hardens: the an stack exists structurally (tables defined in sb, cr tracker connected) but is not operational. socialsnapshots = 0 rows. socialposts = 2 records, both from February 2025 (16 months stale). cr tracker connected but producing zero differentiated signals across all 10 tracked cr. This is no longer a "data latency" or "credentials hypothesis" situation — it is a confirmed data ingestion fl w/ a 4-day persistence record. ka's confidence on the diagnosis is hi; confidence on the specific remedy (ap key? rate limiting? script never deployed?) is lo, but the sb connection works — the bottleneck is upstream.
