T|Novi|2|SS26 Countdown: The cg is now within an estimated 9-19 day window of late June w/ zero pre-cg baselines. The risk escalator from the past four days: June 8 identified the problem → June 9 confirmed it wasn't transient → June 10 declared a dependency → June 11 confirms structural fl. Base rate risk unchanged: 30-40% first-month ROAS underperformance for DTC fashion launches w/o engagement baselines. At fx's £80-120 AOV target, the cost of launching blind compounds w/ each day the pipeline stays offline.
